hey guys, 

i made this map in 4 hours about 10 weeks ago due to work and things i just forgot about the map. spent a good 3 hours fixing it up making it look better and here it is :)

the map is about 4 ts ( sharks ) killing off the cts
sharks move fast and gain hp in the water but are slow and lose hp on high land. 

the cts need to stay alive for 180 seconds then its easyer shotting fish in a ........ well sharks :)

its alot of fun for what its worth great with 3 or more m8s on ts or vent great fun :)
